{"tid":2041875,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"知唔知咩叫「違反承諾」？","createTime":"2020-05-29T13:28:58.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-29T13:40:00.000Z","uid":105567,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"dbaec87e5b32d90f4039af48bede3cca4b6e23d6","tid":2041875,"uid":105567,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-29T13:28:58.000Z","msg":"【國安法壓港】英國或增 BNO 持有人權利 中國外交部：違反承諾<br />\n2020/5/29 &mdash; 19:15<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.thestandnews.com/media/photos/cache/20200529-16_GVjtH_1200x0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thestandnews.com%2Fmedia%2Fphotos%2Fcache%2F20200529-16_GVjtH_1200x0.png&h=e3cad424&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n人大昨日通過決定，授權人大常委訂立香港國安法，引發國際社會關注，英國外相藍韜文表示，若中國堅持訂立國安法，英國會考慮增加 BNO 持有人權利，可免簽逗留在英國一年。中國外交部發言人趙立堅回應時指，英國曾與中國互換備忘錄，明確承諾不給予持有 BNO 的香港中國公民居留權，如果英方執意單方面改變有關做法，不單違背自身立場承諾，也違反國際法和國際關係基本準則，中國堅決反對，會保留採取相應措施權利。<br />\n<br />\n趙立堅又表示，人大常委會關於《國籍法》在港實施的解釋，明確指「香港中國同胞」，無論是持有英國屬土公民護照抑或 BNO，都是中國公民；希望英國公正客觀看待國安法，不會以任何方式干預香港事務。<br />\n<br />\n對於美國國務卿蓬佩奥發聲明，並向國會證實香港不再高度自治，趙立堅質疑蓬佩奥是與港獨及「黑暴」站在一起，嚴重干涉中國内政，強調任何破壞阻撓全國人大訂立港區國安法的行動，都是螳臂擋車注定失敗。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/%E5%9C%8B%E5%AE%89%E6%B3%95%E5%A3%93%E6%B8%AF-%E8%8B%B1%E5%9C%8B%E6%88%96%E5%A2%9E-bno-%E6%8C%81%E6%9C%89%E4%BA%BA%E6%AC%8A%E5%88%A9-%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E5%A4%96%E4%BA%A4%E9%83%A8-%E9%81%95%E5%8F%8D%E6%89%BF%E8%AB%BE/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E5%259C%258B%25E5%25AE%2589%25E6%25B3%2595%25E5%25A3%2593%25E6%25B8%25AF-%25E8%258B%25B1%25E5%259C%258B%25E6%2588%2596%25E5%25A2%259E-bno-%25E6%258C%2581%25E6%259C%2589%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E6%25AC%258A%25E5%2588%25A9-%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%259C%258B%25E5%25A4%2596%25E4%25BA%25A4%25E9%2583%25A8-%25E9%2581%2595%25E5%258F%258D%25E6%2589%25BF%25E8%25AB%25BE%2F&d=nsl8wma01YyMGEZOa9B33HG%2F0kAjhv1dd93UXbk31gU%3D&h=57222357\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E5%259C%258B%25E5%25AE%2589%25E6%25B3%2595%25E5%25A3%2593%25E6%25B8%25AF-%25E8%258B%25B1%25E5%259C%258B%25E6%2588%2596%25E5%25A2%259E-bno-%25E6%258C%2581%25E6%259C%2589%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E6%25AC%258A%25E5%2588%25A9-%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%259C%258B%25E5%25A4%2596%25E4%25BA%25A4%25E9%2583%25A8-%25E9%2581%2595%25E5%258F%258D%25E6%2589%25BF%25E8%25AB%25BE%2F&h=e4ffae8b\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/%E5%9C%8B%E5%AE%89%E6%B3%95%E5%A3%93%E6%B8%AF-%E8%8B%B1%E5%9C%8B%E6%88%96%E5%A2%9E-bno-%E6%8C%81%E6%9C%89%E4%BA%BA%E6%AC%8A%E5%88%A9-%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E5%A4%96%E4%BA%A4%E9%83%A8-%E9%81%95%E5%8F%8D%E6%89%BF%E8%AB%BE/</a>"},{"pid":"40cf78ba7b50bcaec4c3691496a669f6c5b128e6","tid":2041875,"uid":149534,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-29T13:35:36.000Z","msg":"明確指「香港中國同胞」，無論是持有英國屬土公民護照抑或 BNO。<br />\n<br />\n你不如直接話黃皮膚黑眼睛就係中國公民。"},{"pid":"c794a53f725e81b81428b92ad3b7ba928f6d82a8","tid":2041875,"uid":29153,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-29T13:40:00.000Z","msg":"歷史文件，不具任何實際意義"}]}